quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,Have you seen the one who denies this faith
  107,2,For that is the one who drives the orphan away
  107,3,and does not encourage the feeding of the poor
  107,4,So woe to those who pray
  107,5,"but, who do not pay attention to their prayer"
  107,6,"Those who make a show [of their deeds]"
  107,7,and withhold assistance to others